tpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-66k","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":40014,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/05\/12\/kafarah-saqam\/","url_meta":{"origin":23456,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Trials: Allah expiates all sins with sickness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 12, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah will put His servant to trial with illness until that expiates every one of his sins.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 9397 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37802,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/05\/20\/expiation-sickness\/","url_meta":{"origin":23456,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Trials: Expiation of sins due to sickness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 20, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo believing man or woman, nor Muslim man or woman, is afflicted with illness but that Allah will curtail some of their sins by it.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad lil-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 508 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35138,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/01\/allah-expiates-sickness\/","url_meta":{"origin":23456,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Trials: Allah expiates sins with disease","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 1, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Jubayr ibn Mut\u2019im reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty will put His servant to trial by illness until his every sin is expiated.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 1548 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064f\u0637\u0652\u0639\u0650\u0645\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17173,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/13\/believers-put-to-trial-sins\/","url_meta":{"origin":23456,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Trials: Believers put to trial until all sins expiated","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 13, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe believing men and women continue to be under trial in their lives, their children, and their wealth, until they meet Allah without any sin.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2399 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38128,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/08\/15\/afflictions-recompense\/","url_meta":{"origin":23456,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sins: Believers recompensed in the world for their sins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 15, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Bakr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAfflictions, diseases, and sadness in the world are a recompense for sins.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304' 8\/119 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0628\u064e\u0643\u0652\u0631\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0650\u0651\u062f\u0650\u0651\u064a\u0642 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0635\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0628\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0636\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7286,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/29\/punish-trials-this-world\/","url_meta":{"origi